\section Color_attributes
\code
- for surfaces (A) and solids (B) 
- struct ColRGB     type is Typ_Color
- source ../ut/ut_col.c and ../ut/ut_col.h
- ColRGB is used as INT32 for GL-functions (COL_INT32 / INT32_COL)



\endcode
